---

## рҹ§  How It Works

* SQL queries are dynamically generated using Bash
* UI is rendered using `dialog`
* Table data is converted into interactive menus
* CRUD operations are built automatically based on table structure

---

## вҡ пёҸ Security Notice

This project executes SQL queries directly on your database.

* Do not use in production without additional validation
* Prefer using in local or development environments
* Avoid connecting to critical or sensitive databases

